{"id":23854,"date":"2023-03-17T20:21:04","date_gmt":"2023-03-17T16:21:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/?p=23854"},"modified":"2025-03-19T11:05:45","modified_gmt":"2025-03-19T07:05:45","slug":"al-mundhiri-bribery-hukm","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-bribery-hukm\/","title":{"rendered":"Imam al-Mundhiri on Bribery in Judgment"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>In the Name of Allah, the Gracious, the Merciful<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Imam al-Mundhiri recorded the chapter in his book Inspiring Hope and Inciting Fear:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u062a\u0631\u0647\u064a\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u0634\u064a \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u062a\u0634\u064a \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0627\u0639\u064a \u0628\u064e\u064a\u0646\u0647\u0645\u064e\u0627<\/p>\n<p>Warning against giving and taking bribes, and pursuing either of them.<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Targhi\u0304b wal-Tarhi\u0304b 3\/125<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him said:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0634\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0643\u0652\u0645\u0650<\/p>\n<p><strong>Allah has cursed the one who offers a bribe and the one who accepts a bribe to receive a favorable judgment.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 9031, Grade: <strong><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/14\/curses-bribery\/\">Sahih li ghayrihi<\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>In another narration, Abu Huraira said:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0644\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0634\u0650<\/p>\n<p>The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, cursed the one who offers bribes and the one who takes bribes.<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1337, Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Abu al-Ahwas reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said:<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0627\u0644\u0631\u0650\u0651\u0634\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0643\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0643\u064f\u0641\u0652\u0631\u064c \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0633\u064f\u062d\u0652\u062a\u064c<\/p>\n<p>Bribery to receive a favorable judgement is an act of unbelief, and between people it is illicit.<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 9100, Grade: <strong><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/17\/bribery-kufr-asghar\/\">Sahih li ghayrihi<\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><em>Success comes from Allah, and Allah knows best.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&#8220;Warning against giving and taking bribes, and pursuing either of them.&#8221;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-di